%% Diagram: Spanner Commit Wait
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant Coordinator as Coordinator Leader
    participant Replica as Replica
    participant TT as TrueTime API

    Client->>Coordinator: BEGIN T1
    Coordinator->>TT: TT.now()
    TT-->>Coordinator: [earliest, latest], ε≈4 ms
    Note over Coordinator: pick s = TT.now().latest<br/>(commit timestamp)
    Coordinator->>Replica: prepare T1 @ s
    Replica-->>Coordinator: prepared
    Note over Coordinator: COMMIT WAIT:<br/>block until TT.after(s)<br/>≈ 2ε ≈ 7-14 ms
    Coordinator-->>Client: ack T1
    Note right of Coordinator: Any T2 starting after the ack<br/>is guaranteed s(T2) > s(T1)<br/>without any T1↔T2 messaging.
